	<h2>Mission</h2>
	<p>Simply put, our mission is to strengthen and advance the printing industry across Canada. <a href="https://cpia-aci.ca/mission">READ MORE</a></p>
	
</div>



<div class="square square5 clear">

<h2>Members</h2>
<p>Our membership is comprised of both regional and print-sector associations. Collectively we represent hundreds of print and print-related businesses across the country. <a href="https://cpia-aci.ca/member-groups">READ MORE</a></p>

